{"word":"κλέπτης","slug":"κλέπτης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κλέπτης</b></el> <el>(κλέπτης, ου,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κλέπτω'><el>κλέπτω</el></a>\n<p/><i>a thief</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: generally, <i>a cheat, knave</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}